---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getDocBySlug } from '../../../data/navigation';

const doc = getDocBySlug('scheduled-tasks');

if (!doc) {
	throw new Error('Scheduled tasks doc metadata is missing');
}
---

<Layout title={`${doc.title} | 通俗版 Claude Code 文档`} description={doc.summary} pathname={doc.path}>
	<article class="space-y-8">
		<header class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em]" style="color: var(--muted);">Build with Claude Code</p>
			<h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-semibold">Scheduled tasks 定时任务</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8">{doc.summary}</p>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-4xl leading-8" style="color: var(--muted);">
				原页来源：
				<a href="https://code.claude.com/docs/en/scheduled-tasks" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-4">官方 Scheduled tasks</a>
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">一句人话</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>定时任务就是让 Claude 按时自动干活，比如每天早上拉取日报、每周检查依赖更新。</p>
				<p>用 cron 表达式设置时间，到点自动执行指定提示。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">常见用法</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-5 leading-8">
				<div class="rounded-[24px] border p-6" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">每日站会报告</h3>
					<p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">每天早上 9 点自动生成昨日代码变更总结。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-[24px] border p-6" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">依赖检查</h3>
					<p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">每周一检查 npm/pip 依赖更新，生成升级建议。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-[24px] border p-6" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">代码质量报告</h3>
					<p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">每周五分析代码库，生成质量报告和改进建议。</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-[24px] border p-6" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">安全扫描</h3>
					<p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">每天深夜扫描代码，查找潜在安全问题。</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">怎么配置</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>用系统 cron 或 LaunchAgent 定时调用 Claude Code：</p>
				<div class="mt-4 rounded-[24px] border p-6 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
<pre># crontab 示例 - 每天早上 9 点
0 9 * * * claude --print "生成昨日代码变更报告" >> /var/log/claude-daily.log

# macOS LaunchAgent 示例
# ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.claude.daily.plist
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
  <key>Label</key><string>com.claude.daily</string>
  <key>ProgramArguments</key>
  <array>
    <string>claude</string>
    <string>--print</string>
    <string>生成昨日代码变更报告</string>
  </array>
  <key>StartCalendarInterval</key>
  <dict><key>Hour</key><integer>9</integer><key>Minute</key><integer>0</integer></dict>
</dict>
</plist></pre>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">Cron 表达式速查</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8" style="color: var(--muted);">
				<p><code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">0 9 * * *</code> — 每天 9:00</p>
				<p><code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">0 9 * * 1</code> — 每周一 9:00</p>
				<p><code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">0 */2 * * *</code> — 每 2 小时</p>
				<p><code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">0 0 1 * *</code> — 每月 1 号 0:00</p>
				<p><code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">0 9-18 * * 1-5</code> — 工作日 9:00-18:00 每小时</p>
				<p><code class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-code">*/15 * * * *</code> — 每 15 分钟</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">完整示例：每日代码变更报告</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p><strong>步骤 1：创建报告脚本</strong></p>
				<div class="mt-4 rounded-[24px] border p-6 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
<pre>cat > ~/scripts/daily-code-report.sh << 'EOF'
#!/bin/bash
# 每日代码变更报告脚本

cd /path/to/your/project

# 获取昨天的日期
YESTERDAY=$(date -v-1d +%Y-%m-%d)

# 生成报告
claude --print "
分析昨天 ($YESTERDAY) 的代码变更：
1. 列出所有修改的文件
2. 统计新增/删除行数
3. 总结主要改动
4. 指出潜在问题

运行命令获取变更：
git log --since='$YESTERDAY 00:00' --until='$YESTERDAY 23:59' --stat
" > ~/reports/code-report-$YESTERDAY.md

echo "报告已生成：~/reports/code-report-$YESTERDAY.md"
EOF

chmod +x ~/scripts/daily-code-report.sh</pre>
				</div>

				<p><strong>步骤 2：配置定时任务（macOS LaunchAgent）</strong></p>
				<div class="mt-4 rounded-[24px] border p-6 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
<pre>cat > ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.claude.daily-report.plist << 'EOF'
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
  <key>Label</key>
  <string>com.claude.daily-report</string>
  <key>ProgramArguments</key>
  <array>
    <string>/bin/bash</string>
    <string>-l</string>
    <string>-c</string>
    <string>/Users/yourname/scripts/daily-code-report.sh</string>
  </array>
  <key>StartCalendarInterval</key>
  <dict>
    <key>Hour</key>
    <integer>9</integer>
    <key>Minute</key>
    <integer>0</integer>
  </dict>
  <key>StandardOutPath</key>
  <string>/Users/yourname/logs/daily-report.log</string>
  <key>StandardErrorPath</key>
  <string>/Users/yourname/logs/daily-report-error.log</string>
  <key>EnvironmentVariables</key>
  <dict>
    <key>PATH</key>
    <string>/usr/local/bin:/opt/homebrew/bin:/usr/bin:/bin</string>
  </dict>
</dict>
</plist>
EOF

# 加载 LaunchAgent
launchctl load ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.claude.daily-report.plist

# 验证状态
launchctl list | grep daily-report</pre>
				</div>

				<p><strong>步骤 3：配置定时任务（Linux crontab）</strong></p>
				<div class="mt-4 rounded-[24px] border p-6 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
<pre># 编辑 crontab
crontab -e

# 添加以下行（每天 9 点执行）
0 9 * * * /bin/bash -l -c '/home/yourname/scripts/daily-code-report.sh' >> /home/yourname/logs/daily-report.log 2>&1

# 查看 crontab
crontab -l

# 查看 cron 日志（Ubuntu）
grep CRON /var/log/syslog | tail -20</pre>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">注意事项</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p><strong>1. 凭证配置</strong> — 定时任务运行时可能没有交互式环境的凭证，确保已配置好 API key。</p>
				<p><strong>2. 超时处理</strong> — 设置合理超时，防止任务卡住。</p>
				<p><strong>3. 错误处理</strong> — 捕获错误并记录日志，方便排查。</p>
				<p><strong>4. 输出管理</strong> — 定时任务的输出要重定向到文件或发送通知。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">最后一句土话</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>定时任务就是给 Claude 排班，到点自动上班。排好了，省心省力；排不好，半夜吵醒你。</p>
				<p style="color: var(--muted);">建议先从简单的日报开始，慢慢加复杂任务。</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</article>
</Layout>
